  "title": "Existência com が: ある e いる",
  "description": "Lesson 5 of top:n5-verbos. Teaches the subject particle が, the existence verbs ある (inanimate) and いる (animate), the state verbs 開く/閉まる, plus 要る and 借りる, and the kanji 三. Authored to research/derived/lessons/n5-verbos-05.json, validated (well-formed XML, leaf rule respected, no em dash, ends with checklist, 6 exercises with retrieval+production).",
